            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">10 May 1870 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I Beg to hand you the Inclosed account for Tools which were my own property, were used by me for the Bot Gardens and which were stolen from the Engine house on the night that it...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.05.10a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Robertson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">W70/5176, unit 465, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10 May 1870</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I Beg to hand you the Inclosed account for Tools which were my own property, were used by me for the Bot Gardens and which were stolen from the Engine house on the night that it was Broken into in the beginning of March, and request the favour of a speedy Settlement</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">your obt Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>George Robertson</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">care of E. Soues</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Domain Street</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">South Yarra<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The text that follows is on a separate sheet.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>On 10 May,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M noted on the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>verso of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Robertson's letter: 'To ascertain from E. Soues the price or value of these implements'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M sought approval to pay the claim in M to J. McCulloch, 10 May 1870,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and McCulloch minuted his<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>approval on 17 May,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>subject to M's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>satisfying himself that the claim was reasonable.</p>
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Mueller F.R.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Director Bot Gardens</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
